Program: Omnibus
Title: Worse Wars than Belfast
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376js7
Last Broadcast Date: 01 March 1990
***WARNING - This audio contains descriptions of graphic violence***" Young people in Northern Ireland talk about why they love living in Belfast despite the conflict, and how their teenage experiences compare with others around the world. They discuss paramiltary punishments, drugs, alcohol and the British Army. Show less